Package de.rss.fachstudie.MiSim.export

Class ContinuousMultiDataPointReporter

java.lang.Object
desmoj.core.report.Reporter
de.rss.fachstudie.MiSim.export.MultiDataPointReporter
de.rss.fachstudie.MiSim.export.ContinuousMultiDataPointReporter
public class ContinuousMultiDataPointReporter
extends MultiDataPointReporter
MultiDataPointReporter that repeats the last entry before adding a new one. This creates the effect that each entered values plateaus until its updated.

This is specifically use in combination with a line graph.

If you need raw value output see MultiDataPointReporter

Author:
Lion Wagner
